                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p>The dumbbell sumo squat is a highly effective exercise for strengthening the glutes than traditional squats. It also offers a nice reprieve to any squat-heavy training regime thatâs underdelivering results or feeling uninspiring.</p><p>In this article, we cover everything you need to know about this squat variation. Weâll start by outlining proper performance before discussing how it can help you break through workout plateaus.</p>                    </div>
